{"tid":111701,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【啲客仔好開心】豪玩豪食8萬8旅行團 仲有杜如風特别服務?!","createTime":"2017-02-07T14:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T05:33:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c17f52b9a5bdd4290a686e4d305398c3ad58bbf","tid":111701,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T14:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170207/small/1486433229_06c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170207%2Fsmall%2F1486433229_06c4.jpg&h=986ad97b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由杜如風親自率領嘅$88,888，由初二出發去到日本玩五日，當時大家都好好奇，到底呢個8萬8旅行團有啲咩玩，之前杜如風就話咗畀《蘋果》知有咩玩、有咩食等等，而當中最有趣嘅地方，就係取消咗唔少景點嘅行程，而去咗購物。(詳見： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2jWb0Bb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2jWb0Bb&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=1f6f7694\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2jWb0Bb</a> )<br />\n<br />\n而喺今日，呢個8萬8旅行團又有啲特別嘅服務流出咗，<span style=\"color: red;\">因為杜如風喺IG貼咗一條片，就係佢喺旅遊車上面，同一班團友大唱粵曲</span>，睇到佢哋鬼咁開心，仲個個都拎住個電話出嚟拍片，唱唱下杜如風就問佢同行嘅媽媽之後點唱，但係佢媽媽都話唔識，之後就轉另一首粵曲，不過唱咗兩句就冇唱喇。睇嚟8萬8除咗可以豪玩豪食之外，仲可以聽杜如風唱粵曲，一班團友聽得鬼咁開心，杜如風問大家佢唱得掂唔掂嘅時候，一班團友都大叫：「掂啊！」大家又有冇興趣俾8萬8聽歌呢？  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170207/56271661\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170207%2F56271661&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=5d2734d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170207%2F56271661&h=dfddd9cb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170207/56271661</a>"},{"pid":"7b8cb2d51f46b5db9621d90dd9c8cc1d63748aeb","tid":111701,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14e20e282d353c7600dc29439be0daba2accdae","tid":111701,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T15:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d959e15cf9cba568228722d9cb9aa8b737dfd4fb","tid":111701,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31041082ef156320741cc338f0367b2943302d26","tid":111701,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T18:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c130823ba0e8e56eeba33a4f807021839e03f81","tid":111701,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc80fe71cec98164d205219516e8c71c892a8f8","tid":111701,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/09/133304_669a0668951a0f1a5ff7695384eda57a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F09%2F133304_669a0668951a0f1a5ff7695384eda57a.jpg&h=08d29d97&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}